             was indicted for <rs id="t18310630-312-off1631" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310630-312-off1631" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310630-312-off1631" type="offenceSubcategory" value="receiving"></interp>
               feloniously receiving, on the <rs id="t18310630-312-cd1632" type="crimeDate">25th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310630-312-off1631 t18310630-312-cd1632"></join>, 2 pairs of breeches, value 5s.; 2 pairs of trousers, value 5s.; 1 pair of drawers, value 1s.; 1 coat, value 3s.; 2 waistcoats, value 1s.; 2 shawls, value 2s.; 1 gown, value 1s.; 4 petticoats, value 1s., and 2 frocks, value 1s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18310630-312-victim2195" type="victimName">
                        Hugh 
                        Cox
                     <interp inst="t18310630-312-victim2195" type="surname" value="Cox"></interp>
